<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22UND9UJ4N%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B318.446%2C478.739%2C545.849%2C485.48%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C468.317%2C481.311%2C475.058%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D">“Algoritmos e inteligência artificial têm o potencial de apoiar os tomadores de decisão no governo, principalmente no orçamento público.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 12</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22Q5836AVN%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B419.148%2C457.838%2C528.542%2C464.579%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C447.416%2C546.52%2C454.157%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C436.937%2C545.725%2C443.678%5D%2C%5B306.634%2C426.515%2C503.326%2C433.256%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D">“baseada principalmente em análises estatísticas, nossa análise de dados baseada em IA recomendou que o governo considere certas despesas orçamentárias públicas para melhorar o crescimento econômico, reduzir a inflação e diminuir a desigualdade de renda.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 12</span>)</span></p>
