<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22WDGXV76A%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B318.661%2C332.432%2C542.701%2C339.173%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C321.954%2C518.385%2C328.694%5D%2C%5B306.666%2C311.619%2C532.579%2C318.36%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C301.052%2C474.186%2C307.793%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D">“Devido à complexidade inerente à política fiscal, causada por fatores como crises econômicas, pandemias, taxas de câmbio e interesses políticos, consideramos que a distribuição do gasto público deve ser dinâmica, pois o ambiente em que ele está inserido também é dinâmico .”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 12</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%227T2TWK3E%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B531.912%2C280.151%2C551.77%2C286.892%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C269.729%2C540.144%2C276.47%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C259.25%2C543.116%2C265.991%5D%2C%5B306.618%2C248.828%2C383.792%2C255.569%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D">“alguns dos principais benefícios do uso da IA na alocação de gastos públicos vêm de fornecer orientação ou critérios de alocação para alavancar objetivos múltiplos, muitas vezes conflitantes.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 12</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22HWUQDUEF%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B385.666%2C248.828%2C555.011%2C255.569%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C238.349%2C554.737%2C245.09%5D%2C%5B306.562%2C227.927%2C475.914%2C234.668%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D">“Apesar da caixa preta inerente aos algoritmos de IA, tais técnicas podem trazer algum grau de racionalidade ao processo orçamentário, que não é apenas de natureza técnica, mas também política.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 12</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22ERYJXRCE%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2212%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A11%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B306.578%2C133.845%2C542.609%2C140.585%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C123.422%2C553.982%2C130.162%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C112.943%2C560.743%2C119.684%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%7D">“Eles devem estar cientes de que seu potencial nem sempre pode ser realizado como tomada automática de decisões, mas no apoio a formas criativas de analisar e entender os dados usados para programas e políticas governamentais específicos.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2212%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 12</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22K3WY6Y5P%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B83.842%2C720.559%2C281.694%2C727.127%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C710.049%2C277.333%2C716.617%5D%2C%5B37.785%2C699.57%2C281.625%2C706.138%5D%2C%5B37.777%2C689.148%2C269.197%2C695.716%5D%2C%5B37.682%2C678.669%2C68.708%2C685.237%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“Com base na abordagem de Kurzweil, isso poderia ser chamado de máquina de orçamento inteligente. No entanto, sabemos que o uso de inteligência artificial nem sempre significa que os tomadores de decisão humanos não são mais necessários e isso é particularmente verdadeiro em processos políticos como o orçamento”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%224LQAFPS8%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B190.433%2C647.346%2C283.513%2C653.914%5D%2C%5B37.729%2C636.867%2C284.866%2C643.435%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C626.445%2C263.809%2C633.013%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“Um sistema de IA automatizado que toma decisões técnicas para serem aceitas por políticos ou outros tomadores de decisão ainda está longe de ser tecnicamente possível e politicamente viável.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%226G8KJGJ9%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B137.857%2C605.544%2C283.881%2C612.112%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C595.065%2C289.733%2C601.633%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C584.643%2C285.339%2C591.211%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C574.164%2C285.713%2C580.732%5D%2C%5B37.753%2C563.742%2C287.084%2C570.31%5D%2C%5B37.729%2C553.263%2C269.189%2C559.831%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C542.841%2C269.661%2C549.409%5D%2C%5B37.785%2C532.45%2C259.012%2C539.018%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C521.94%2C77.99%2C528.508%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“possíveis efeitos na sociedade para os tomadores de decisão ou seus funcionários. Uma vez que essa informação é gerada, ela se torna parte de um processo de tomada de decisão mais complexo, um processo altamente político e às vezes até irracional. A esse respeito, a IA não é diferente de um sistema de apoio à decisão ou de um modelo estatístico, pois fornecem informações úteis. No entanto, o tomador de decisão final ainda pode ignorar seus resultados. Apesar dessa situação, defendemos que todas essas ferramentas e técnicas ainda são relevantes e úteis para determinados atores e situações dentro do processo orçamentário.”</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22A7JJ2AWR%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B191.884%2C417.465%2C284.242%2C424.033%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C406.956%2C281.681%2C413.524%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C396.477%2C258.706%2C403.045%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“Reconhecemos que o processo orçamentário é complexo, mas defendemos que a inteligência artificial pode auxiliar na tomada de decisões, principalmente do ponto de vista técnico e racional.”</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%225DCUZ7F2%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B175.756%2C313.956%2C275.765%2C320.524%5D%2C%5B37.729%2C302.451%2C275.014%2C309.019%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C291.972%2C269.307%2C298.54%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C281.55%2C285.359%2C288.118%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C271.071%2C283.513%2C277.639%5D%2C%5B37.841%2C260.649%2C222.918%2C267.217%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“De forma mais geral, algumas das vantagens que as técnicas de inteligência artificial oferecem estão relacionadas à capacidade de analisar qualquer dado, independentemente de sua distribuição, tamanho ou formato. No entanto, algumas limitações da tomada de decisão baseada em IA estão relacionadas à capacidade computacional necessária para implementar algumas dessas técnicas e à falta de transparência algorítmica.”</span></p>
<p>“A primeira situação é um problema potencial para as agências governamentais, particularmente nos níveis local e estadual. Devem possuir sólida infraestrutura computacional de processamento e armazenamento e pessoal treinado em inteligência artificial e/ou ciência de dados. Além disso, eles exigem uma quantidade significativa de tempo para realizar esses tipos de simulações antes de obter alguns benefícios potenciais, particularmente aqueles relacionados a uma melhor tomada de decisão. Por esses motivos, o orçamento inteligente vai além de apenas uma abordagem algorítmica. Depende de muitos fatores e diversas partes interessadas para ser verdadeiramente inteligente.” <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
<p>“As limitações desta pesquisa estão relacionadas ao fato de que poderíamos não incluir em um algoritmo toda a complexidade do processo orçamentário em termos econômicos, políticos e humanos.” <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22TCEZRXAH%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B429.314%2C626.532%2C545.395%2C633.1%5D%2C%5B306.665%2C615.966%2C544.305%2C622.534%5D%2C%5B306.61%2C605.544%2C422.678%2C612.112%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“Conforme mencionado anteriormente, o processo orçamentário não é um exercício puramente técnico, e há muitos atores interessados em si mesmos envolvidos.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%227RD87D6L%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B360.394%2C542.841%2C554.259%2C549.409%5D%2C%5B306.681%2C532.362%2C544.689%2C538.93%5D%2C%5B306.562%2C521.94%2C548.208%2C528.508%5D%2C%5B306.57%2C511.461%2C549.714%2C518.029%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C501.039%2C545.451%2C507.606%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C490.56%2C329.716%2C497.128%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“Uma das vantagens da IA é encontrar padrões no banco de dados analisado e, assim, distribuir o orçamento considerando a alocação do orçamento público que os governos implementaram para alcançar o crescimento econômico e reduzir a inflação e a desigualdade. No entanto, a análise de um único país poderia permitir compreender seu contexto e situação particular de forma mais profunda e precisa.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22ETNE2E4B%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%2213%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A12%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B306.57%2C355.145%2C551.5%2C361.713%5D%2C%5B306.618%2C344.341%2C544.711%2C350.909%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C333.774%2C555.323%2C340.342%5D%2C%5B306.666%2C323.352%2C542.841%2C329.92%5D%2C%5B306.658%2C312.873%2C548.317%2C319.441%5D%2C%5B306.634%2C302.451%2C545.009%2C309.019%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C291.972%2C551.651%2C298.54%5D%2C%5B306.53%2C281.55%2C555.848%2C288.118%5D%2C%5B306.666%2C271.159%2C346.815%2C277.726%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%7D">“Por isso, pesquisas futuras devem avaliar essas técnicas em contextos particulares, adaptar-se às necessidades específicas de diferentes nações e governos e incluir outros fatores inerentes ao orçamento público. Outro caminho para pesquisas futuras consiste em simular diferentes cenários com modelos de IA para entender outras possíveis relações entre gastos do orçamento público e outros resultados sociais e econômicos úteis para a tomada de decisões do governo. Finalmente, seria muito interessante comparar diretamente as técnicas de IA com modelos estatísticos mais tradicionais em termos de seus resultados e possíveis recomendações para alocação orçamentária.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%2213%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 13</span>)</span></p>
