20aspects%20of%20the%20expenditure%20allocation%20process%20could%20be%20improved%20with%20the%20help%20of%20these%20kinds%20of%20techniques.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20results%20of%20the%20AI%20based%20approach%20are%20consistent%20with%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20scientific%20literature%20on%20public%20budgets%2C%20using%20traditional%20statistical%20techniques.%22%2C%22container-title%22%3A%22Government%20Information%20Quarterly%22%2C%22DOI%22%3A%2210.1016%2Fj.giq.2021.101644%22%2C%22ISSN%22%3A%220740-624X%22%2C%22issue%22%3A%222%22%2C%22journalAbbreviation%22%3A%22Government%20Information%20Quarterly%22%2C%22language%22%3A%22en%22%2C%22page%22%3A%22101644%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22DOI.org%20(Crossref)%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22From%20E-budgeting%20to%20smart%20budgeting%3A%20Exploring%20the%20potential%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20government%20decision-making%20for%20resource%20allocation%22%2C%22title-short%22%3A%22From%20E-budgeting%20to%20smart%20budgeting%22%2C%22URL%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com%2Fretrieve%2Fpii%2FS0740624X21000800%22%2C%22volume%22%3A%2239%22%2C%22author%22%3A%5B%7B%22family%22%3A%22Valle-Cruz%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22David%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Fernandez-Cortez%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22Vanessa%22%7D%2C%7B%22family%22%3A%22Gil-Garcia%22%2C%22given%22%3A%22J.%20Ramon%22%7D%5D%2C%22accessed%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222023%22%2C5%2C14%5D%5D%7D%2C%22issued%22%3A%7B%22date-parts%22%3A%5B%5B%222022%22%2C4%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22valle-cruzEbudgetingSmartBudgeting2022%22%7D%7D%5D" data-schema-version="8"><p>Vantagens da IA: reconhecimento de padrões;</p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%221%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B351.353%2C401.604%2C552.468%2C407.468%5D%2C%5B202.448%2C392.032%2C555.131%2C397.896%5D%2C%5B202.054%2C382.516%2C341.549%2C388.38%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%7D">“As vantagens da implementação deste tipo de sistema de apoio à decisão na afetação das despesas públicas decorrem da capacidade de processar grandes quantidades de dados e de encontrar padrões de difícil deteção, que incluem múltiplas relações não lineares.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%221%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 1</span>)</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight" data-annotation="%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2FK4FEFN2B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22WP7UZRNP%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23ffd400%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%223%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A2%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B306.761%2C364.77%2C539.255%2C370.849%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C354.291%2C547.654%2C360.371%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C343.869%2C531.099%2C349.949%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C333.391%2C549.131%2C339.47%5D%2C%5B306.721%2C322.968%2C445.272%2C329.047%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%223%22%7D%7D">“Diante disso, a IA tem o potencial de analisar dados relacionados a algumas ações do governo e crescimento econômico, bem como avaliar alguns eventos que podem afetar a alocação dos gastos públicos. Algumas técnicas de IA podem explorar uma grande quantidade de dados e encontrar padrões para detectar situações semelhantes/diferentes úteis para a assistência de alocação de orçamento.”</span> <span class="citation" data-citation="%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2F11261961%2Fitems%2F5N4VM3B9%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%223%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D">(<span class="citation-item">Valle-Cruz et al., 2022, p. 3</span>)</span></p>
